o (''[[Phone Swap]]'') * Ekene Okoye Mpon (''Kiss and the Brides'') * Yolanda Okereke & Aminat Olateju (''[[Journey to Self]]'') * Wanger Ayu & Rosaline Ijejem (''Mr & Mrs'') * Iyen Agbonifo (''[[Adesuwa]]'') |- | valign="top" | {{Award category|#EEDD82|Best Make-up}} * '''Jennifer Alegieuno (''[[The Meeting (film)|The Meeting]]'')''' * Temisan Etsede – ''[[Adesuwa]]'' * Touch of Glamour- Tobi Jeje- Phillip & Korede Olowoyo (''Journey to Self'') * Tracy Iyoha (''The Gods are still not to Blame'') * Olivia Obasi (''Broken'') | valign="top" | {{Award category|#EEDD82|Best Set Design}} * '''Sango B’ Song (''[[Last Flight to Abuja]]'')''' * Pat Nebo (''[[Phone Swap]]'') * Adeoye Bakare (''Heros & Zeros'') * Hilary Patrick (''The Meeting'') |- | valign="top" | {{Award category|#EEDD82|Best Sound Track}} * '''[[Password (Producer)|Patrick Mathias]] (''[[Hoodrush]]'')''' * Truth (''The Meeting'') * Luke Corradine (''Last flight to Abuja'') * Slam (''Udeme Mmi'') * Truth (''[[Phone Swap]]'') * Oludare Olateju (''The Gods are still not to Blame'') | valign="top" | {{Award category|#EEDD82|Best Diaspora Movie}} * '''''[[Man on Ground]]''''' * ''Alaalo'' * ''[[Turning Point (2012 film)]]'' * ''The Past came Calling'' * ''Secret Past'' |- | valign="top" | {{Award category|#EEDD82|Best Short Movie}} * '''''Unspoken''''' * ''15 Minutes'' * ''Epitaph'' * ''Ogondah'' * ''Blink'' * ''Till Death do us Apart'' | valign="top" | {{Award category|#EEDD82|Best Rising Star (male)}} * '''[[Uti Nwachukwu]] (''In the Cupboard'')''' * OC Ukeje – Hoodrush * Ifeanyi Kalu (''[[Kokomma]]'') * Bobby Obodo – (''Mrs Somebody'') |- | valign="top" | {{Award category|#EEDD82|Best Rising Star (female)}} * '''[[Belinda Effah]] (''[[Kokomma]]'')''' * [[Linda Ejiofor]] (''The Meeting'') * Ijeoma Agu (''Hoodrush'') * Rachel Isaac (''Daisy'') * Tehila Adiele (''[[Broken (2013 film)]]'') * Tess Abubakar (''In the cupboard'') | valign="top" | {{Award category|#EEDD82|Best child Actor}} * '''Ayomide Abati (''[[Maami]]'')''' * Adeola Faseyi (''[[Married but Living Single]]'') * Regina Ojeogwu (''Wave of Glory'') * Obiora Samuel Olife (''Broken Silence'') |- | valign="top" | {{Award category|#EEDD82|Popular online Choice (male)}} * Imeh Bishop Udoh | valign="top" | {{Award category|#EEDD82|Popular online Choice (female)}} * [[Omotola Jalade Ekeinde]] |- | valign="top" | {{Award category|#EEDD82|Top Box office Movie}} * [[Phone Swap]] | valign="top" | {{Award category|#EEDD82|Industry Patron Award}} * [[Godswill Akpabio|Godswill Obot Akpabio]] |- | colspan="2" | {{Award category|#EEDD82|[[Goodluck Jonathan]] Lifetime Achievement Award: [[Justus Esiri]]}} |}
